trans-unit.source: Represents a single item of data extracted from a workflow and all its associated annotations.
trans-unit.target: Representa um único item dos dados extraídos de um fluxo de trabalho e todas as anotações associadas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a track point, it sends a tracking record to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Quando a infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução corresponde a um ponto de registo, envia um registo de controlo para o serviço de controlo.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> may contain <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects that specify data to be extracted from the workflow and returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> or the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>ou um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>pode conter <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>os <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objetos que especificar dados a ser extraído do fluxo de trabalho e devolvido no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> ou</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: A TrackingDataItem represents a single item of this extracted data in either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Um TrackingDataItem representa um único item destes dados extraídos na ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the list of annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Obtém e define a lista de associados com os dados extraídos de anotações.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> can specify annotations to be sent with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>ou um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>pode especificar anotações para serem enviadas com os dados extraídos.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: These are contained in the Annotations property.
trans-unit.target: Estes são contidos na propriedade anotações.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> que contém as associados com os dados extraídos de anotações.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the extracted data associated with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define os dados extraídos associados a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Data contains the member data, specified by an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> or a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, that was extracted from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Os dados contêm os dados de membro, especificados por uma <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>ou um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>, que foi extraído da instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the extracted data.
Gets or sets the name of the property or field associated with the extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome da propriedade ou campo associados com os dados extraídos.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure supports data extraction on fields and properties of classes that inherit from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; a member of such a field or property; and a single item of a field or a property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface, for example a single element in a collection.
trans-unit.target: A infraestrutura de controlo do tempo de execução suporta a extração de dados em campos e propriedades de classes que herdam <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>; um membro dessa um campo ou propriedade; e um único item de um campo ou uma propriedade (ou um membro do), que implementa o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>interface, por exemplo, um único elemento numa coleção.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: FieldName contains the dot delineated name of the item extracted and is equivalent to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> depending on which type of extract specified the data contained by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.
trans-unit.target: FieldName contém o nome de delineated do ponto do item extraídos e é equivalente ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>os dados contido <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> dependendo do tipo de extração especificado</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: The dot delineated name of the property or field that was extracted.
trans-unit.target: O ponto delimitados nome da propriedade ou campo extraído.
